Once UI Pro
The following section describes the commercial terms of the Once UI Pro subscription and applies in addition to the Dopler CC license.
Grants access to a single editor. If your product is maintained by more than one editor, you need to purchase a Pro license for each editor.

1. Contents
Access to all Once UI Pro repositories on GitHub and access to our copy-paste blocks on once-ui.com.

2. Distribution
