3. Subscription and Updates
Maintaining an active subscription guarantees your access to all upcoming updates. You can cancel your subscription at any point; rest assured, you will continue to receive updates until the end of your current billing cycle. Additionally, an active subscription secures your yearly rate, ensuring that any future price increases will not affect your current subscription cost.

4. Subscription
This is a subscription-based product, subject to yearly renewal. Be aware that upon cancellation, you will no longer receive updates after the current billing period concludes.

